<h2>What Is On Trend?</h2>
<p>On Trend is a social sharing platform that is dedicated to sharing fashion.</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>At On Trend we have two missions:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Help people discover new styles.</li>
  <li>Give any person the opportunity to make money as an influencer through affiliated marketing.</li>
</ol>

<h2>How Do You Make Money?</h2>
<p>Through affiliated marketing. Simply add your link with your affiliated code to the URL section of each article of clothing and users have the option of buying clothes through that link, giving you a percentage of the sale.</p>

